BAND AND ALBUM INFO (English):

Three Days Grace is a Canadian rock band formed in Norwood, Ontario. Human is the upcoming fifth studio album from Canadian rock band Three Days Grace. Scheduled for release on March 31, 2015, the album will be released through RCA Records. This will be the group's first album to feature new vocalist Matt Walst, who replaced Adam Gontier in 2013.
